<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/defence-infrastructure-organisation> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "The Defence Infrastructure Organisation (DIO) is the estate expert for defence, supporting the armed forces to enable military capability by planning, building, maintaining, and servicing infrastructure. DIO is part of the Ministry of Defence ."@en .
